snippet.title: Jack Holmes: Master Of Puppets - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
See gameplay, creepy enemies, and some of the features, like minigames and more, in this trailer for Jack Holmes: Master Of Puppets, an upcoming first-person survival horror game. Jack Holmes: Master Of Puppets will be available in 2024 on Xbox Series X, PlayStation 5, and PC. 

In Jack Holmes: Master Of Puppets, manage your ammunition well, explore varied scenarios, and face nightmarish beings while investigating the macabre experiments with children, the result of a mind unhinged by madness and family loss.

#IGN #Gaming
